./sdp/verification/t-010@20260408t223256zc-verify.md:24:`local_status_display` is in `CypherClawArt` (scenes.py:221), keeping display logic centralized per the spec. `_safe_ollama_health()` wraps `ollama_health()` in a `try/except`, satisfying the degradation requirement. `/local` is registered in `BUILTIN_COMMANDS` (line 1831).
./sdp/verification/t-010@20260408t223256zc-verify.md:50:- `_safe_ollama_health` isolates exception handling cleanly; no bare `except` swallows unexpected errors silently beyond returning a typed fallback dict.
