./sdp/logs/Lead_T-010_20260408T223256Zc_1775694627.log:1579:./sdp/verification/t-007@20260408t223256z-verify.md:17:1. **Unhealthy Ollama excluded from candidate list** — `QuotaMonitor._runtime_unavailable_agents()` calls `_refresh_local_provider_status()` on every `get_available_agents()` invocation. When `ollama_health.check_health()` returns `False` for all configured ports, the local provider is blocked and all agents mapped to it are added to the `blocked` set. These are excluded before both the healthy/warn filter and the fallback max-headroom selection.
