./sdp/logs/Lead_T-010_20260408T223256Zc_1775694627.log:1589:./sdp/verification/t-007@20260408t223256z-verify.md:44:No security concerns. The `importlib.import_module("agent_selector")` call inside `_local_provider_ports` reuses an already-imported module from the same path — no new import-path attack surface beyond what existed before. No secrets, credentials, or user-controlled input flows into health check calls. `ollama_health.check_health(port)` takes an integer port, not a URL derived from external input.
